\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{a\leftarrow m,k}=\dfrac{\sum_{b\in source(m)}\phi_{b\leftarrow m,k}+\sum_{b\in sink(m)}\phi_{m\rightarrow b,k}}{outdeg(m)+indeg(m)}$
\end_inset


